en_6352437_0	At least six persons have been injured following a high speed collision between two buses at Panchikawatta junction in Maradana on Friday morning.
en_6352437_1	News1st’s Krishan Devasagayam reported on the incident.
en_6352437_2	When News 1st contacted the police, they said that the number of injured has risen to 13, and that the injuries are minor.
en_6352437_3	Police added that the wreckage has been moved from the site, and that the traffic flow in the area has returned to normalcy.
